{"tid":533012,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《老師！、、、我可以喜歡你嗎？》討論區","createTime":"2018-01-18T11:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T15:01:07.000Z","uid":167086,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f78ae2e9838ea859ff861221e69b8cd28961d5","tid":533012,"uid":167086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"演員\t生田斗真, 廣瀨鈴, 龍星涼, 森川葵, 健太郎, 比嘉愛未<br />\n語言\t日語<br />\n級別\tIIA<br />\n導演\t三木孝浩<br />\n片長\t113 分鐘<br />\n類型\t劇情、愛情<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">故事簡介</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n高校2年級生響（廣瀨鈴飾），一直旁觀着憧憬戀愛的同班同學惠（森川葵飾）和浩介（龍星涼飾），直至察覺任教世界史的伊藤老師（生田斗真飾）&mdash;&mdash;冷淡、不苟言笑、會躺在長櫈午睡而忘記授課、明明不是班主任卻在課後替她補習。「我可以喜歡你嗎？」「不要喜歡我。」就算被拒絕了，響還是情不自禁地喜歡着伊藤老師。為了「被撤底的拒絕」，響相約伊藤老師到學校天台，但她不知道伊藤老師已動了心，更抱着她吻了下去&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Trailer</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XaGAkOfN3m4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXaGAkOfN3m4&d=6AgurqSXUKIqbV6VfhvAGviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=62cdfcc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XaGAkOfN3m4</a>"},{"pid":"19aea3627dbef1d101bc6064357e49ba8579b7d7","tid":533012,"uid":167086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"拍得幾好，帶出咗唔少現實社會嘅情況<br />\n不過高潮位唔夠衝擊，劇情好容易估到<br />\n同埋落雨果part睇到好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"> 広瀬すず好靚女，我女神</span></span>"},{"pid":"fcdf1c0cfb6f1a33b9ff5a600fc5360e10345895","tid":533012,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"腥些 二拜打士嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f3e00364d0552b68fb11225693bcf401709433","tid":533012,"uid":167086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite